🧠 Data Sentinel

A data quality, drift detection, and AI insights platform built with FastAPI, PostgreSQL, and Streamlit.

It transforms raw CSV datasets into structured insights including:

Data profiling
Column health scoring
Schema + distribution drift detection
AI-generated data insights (optional)
Historical dataset tracking
🚀 Key Features
📊 Data Profiling Engine
Row & column statistics
Missing value detection
Duplicate row detection
Memory usage estimation
Automatic type inference
🧠 Column Health Scoring

Each column is classified into:

🟢 good → clean and usable
🟡 warning → moderate missingness
🔴 bad → fully null or schema issue

Detects:

Fully null columns
High missing rate (>30%)
Broken schema columns (Unnamed)
🔄 Dataset Drift Detection

Compares datasets over time:

Schema drift (added/removed columns)
Type drift (data type changes)
Distribution drift (mean/std shifts)
Row growth or shrinkage
🤖 AI Insights (Optional)

Powered by OpenAI:

Data quality interpretation
Risk identification
Cleaning recommendations

Graceful fallback behavior:

No API key → disabled safely
Quota exceeded → fallback message
API errors → non-blocking system
📈 Streamlit Dashboard
Upload CSV files
View dataset health score
Visualize missing values
Inspect column health
Browse historical reports
🏗️ System Architecture
Frontend (Streamlit)
        ↓
FastAPI Backend
        ↓
Data Processing Layer (Pandas / Profiler / Drift Engine)
        ↓
PostgreSQL (Dataset storage + reports)
        ↓
OpenAI API (optional AI insights)
